snippet.title: C/C++ Dublin User Group
snippet.description:
A group of professional developers and hobbyists living and working in Dublin, Ireland who meet monthly to discuss trends, techniques, and technologies related to the C and C++ languages and industry. This group is open to anyone and everyone. Meet other C and C++ enthusiasts, learn something new and share your knowledge and experience.

https://www.meetup.com/cppdug/
